                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Sherman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1897-11-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 5, 1897</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Brazilian soldier attempted to assassinate the President to day. Minister of war,
                    defending him, was killed. Great excitement, but not general alarm.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Conger.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
